	('0863334a-f10a-47b3-a84f-4f426124a016', 'Albion.Arbiter.WhisperReceive.Text5', 'Oh yes, the inhabitants. It seems, well, at one point, there were no societies of creatures in the planes. That was our first mistake. We assumed there would only be the trials. It turns out that somehow, the creatures of the Planes, after Atlantis\' fall, found the means to survive in the planes. We think some creatures may have even escaped to the planes, though we can\'t be sure. All we know is that when Atlantis fell, it fell quickly. But, as for what lies beyond that portal, all I can say is the trials still [exist].', 'Oh ja, die Einwohner. Zu einem Zeitpunkt sah es so aus, als hÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¤tte es keine Gesellschaftsformen unter den Kreaturen in den Ebenen gegeben. Das war unser erster Fehler. Wir dachten, es gÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¤be nur PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen. Es zeigte sich, dass irgendwie, nach dem Fall Atlantis. die Kreaturen von den Ebenen einen Weg fanden, in den Ebenen zu ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼berleben. Wir glauben, dass manche Kreaturen sogar in den Ebenen Zuflucht suchten, doch wir kÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¶nnen uns nicht sicher sein. Alles was wir wissen ist, dass als Atlantis fiel, fiel es schnell. Doch ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼ber das, was hinter dem Portal liegt, kann ich nur sagen, dass die PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen noch immer [existieren].', 'Oh yes, the inhabitants. It seems, well, at one point, there were no societies of creatures in the planes. That was our first mistake. We assumed there would only be the trials. It turns out that somehow, the creatures of the Planes, after Atlantis\' fall, found the means to survive in the planes. We think some creatures may have even escaped to the planes, though we can\'t be sure. All we know is that when Atlantis fell, it fell quickly. But, as for what lies beyond that portal, all I can say is the trials still [exist].', '', NULL, NULL, '', ''),
