	('9474e18a-a17e-4bf3-9658-85071b8132ae', 'Hibernia.Arbiter.WhisperReceive.Text4', 'It is the Hall of Heroes. As the Atlanteans refer to it. It\'s the entrance to the Planes of Trials. Now, I can glean a bit off of these tablets. We know that beyond this, throught that portal there, lies tha Planes of Trials. There are some trials you must defeat if you wish to be considered worthy of Atlantis. To fail is to die, for the most part, though it does mention something about survivors being sent away in disgrace. I can\'t tell you much about the trials, or even how to pass them. You see, Atlantis has fallen, and of the first ones we sent into the planes, only a few [survived].', 'Es ist die Halle der Helden, wie die Atlanter sie nannten. Es ist der Eingang zu den Ebenen der PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen. Nun, ein wenig kann ich diesen Tafeln entnehmen. Wir wissen, hinter dem Portal dort liegen die Ebenen der PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen. Es gibt einige PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen, die Ihr bestehen mÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼sst, wenn Ihr fÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼r Atlantis als wÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼rdig angesehen werden wollt. Versagen bedeutet meistens zu sterben. Obwohl auch von ÃƒÆ’Ã…â€œberlebenden berichtet wird, die in Schande fortgeschickt wurden. Ich kann Euch nicht viel ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼ber die PrÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼fungen sagen, oder wie sie zu bestehen sind. Atlantis fiel, und von denen, die wir als erstes in die Ebenen aussandten, wissen wir, dass nur wenige [ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¼berlebt] haben.', 'It is the Hall of Heroes. As the Atlanteans refer to it. It\'s the entrance to the Planes of Trials. Now, I can glean a bit off of these tablets. We know that beyond this, throught that portal there, lies tha Planes of Trials. There are some trials you must defeat if you wish to be considered worthy of Atlantis. To fail is to die, for the most part, though it does mention something about survivors being sent away in disgrace. I can\'t tell you much about the trials, or even how to pass them. You see, Atlantis has fallen, and of the first ones we sent into the planes, only a few [survived].', '', NULL, NULL, '', ''),
