	('greetingsArmsmanDescription', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description', 'Continue to speak with Captain Kinzee.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescription1', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description1', 'As an Armsman you have a wide array of combat specialization available to you. [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], and [Polearm]. You may ask me about any of these specializations. A word of caution however, try and limit yourself from spreading out your training. You will never master the ways of combat, if you don\'t focus yourself. When you are [done], I have something for you.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionCrush', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Crush', 'Crush is a basic weaponry skill. Each train you place into it will increase your damage with a crushing weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to crushing weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], [Polearm] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionDone', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Done', 'Very well then, remember you can come to me at any time to ask about your specializations if you need.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionPolearm', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Polearm', 'Polearm is an advanced weaponry skill. When training this, you should also train a basic weaponry skill to pair with it. Polearms come in every basic type: Thrust, Crush, and Slash. Polearms are also two-handed weapons. While using polearm, you will not be able to hold a shield. Your benefit in this weaponry types ability to create massive damage. But you will also be left more vulnerable without a shield. What else can I tell you about? [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], [Polearm] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionShield', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Shield', 'Training your shield specialization will increase your ability to block an enemy\'s attacks. What most do not know is, it can also be used offensivly in the right situations. Traing shield will grant you shield specific combat styles at various levels. [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], [Polearm] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionSlash', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Slash', 'Slash is a basic weaponry skill. Each train you place into it will increase your damage with a slashing weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to slashing weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], [Polearm] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsArmsmanDescriptionThrust', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Description.Thrust', 'Thrust is a basic weaponry skill. Each train you place into it will increase your damage with a thrusting weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to thrusting weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Thrust], [Crush], [Slash], [Shield], [Polearm] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
