	('greetingsArmsmanStory', 'Alb.GreetingsArmsman.Story', 'Greetings, Armsman. I see you are new here. Let me assure you, you\'ve picked the right profession. There\'s nothing like donning your armor for battle, and rushing in with sword held high. Tell me, do you understand what all of your skills do? I can explain each one for you. I shall even make this worth your while.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
