	('greetingsMaulerAlbStory', 'Alb.GreetingsMaulerAlb.Story', 'Welcome to Holtham and Constantine\'s Sound, (Your Name). I am Harbuses, Minotaur Mauler. I am glad you have decided to join our ranks. We are amongst some of the fiercest warriors Albion has seen. Allow me to introduce you to our different specializations. When finished, I should be able to find a few items for you to choose from as a reward. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
