	('greetingsMercenaryConclusionText2', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Conclusion.Text2', 'Remember you can always return to me and ask about these specializations by name. Now for that reward.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMercenaryDescriptionCrush', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Description.Crush', 'Crush is a basic weaponry skill. Each train you place into it will increase your damage with a crushing weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to crushing weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Crush], [Thrust], [Slash], [Dual wield], [Shield], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMercenaryDescriptionDone', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Description.Done', 'Very well, remember you can always return to me and ask about these specializations by name. Now for that reward.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMercenaryDescriptionDualWield', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Description.DualWield', 'Training dual wield will allow you to hit with both of your weapons more often. It will also provide you with specialized combat styles, that require you to have two weapons readied. Training it will increase the damage of those styles as well. You will not be able to hold a shield while you have a weapon in both hands. You will benefit from its extra damage, but in return be more vulnerable without a shield. What else can I tell you about? [Crush], [Thrust], [Slash], [Dual wield], [Shield], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMercenaryDescriptionMain', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Description.Main', 'As a mercenary you have many specializations to choose from. [Crush], [Thrust], [Slash], [Dual wield], and [Shield]. I can tell you about any of these specializations. When you are [done] let me know.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMercenaryDescriptionShield', 'Alb.GreetingsMercenary.Description.Shield', 'Training your shield specialization will increase your ability to block an enemy\'s attacks. What most do not know is, it can also be used offensively in the right situations. Training shield will grant you shield specific combat styles at various levels. What else can I tell you about? [Crush], [Thrust], [Slash], [Dual wield], [Shield], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
