	('greetingsMinstrelDescriptionInstruments', 'Alb.GreetingsMinstrel.Description.Instruments', 'Training instruments will increase the damage of musical spells and offers speed, health and mana songs, that increase your regeneration of each. Included in this line are memorizations spells, which will hold your enemy captive during combat. What else can I tell you about? [Stealth], [Slash], [Thrust], [Instruments], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMinstrelDescriptionMain', 'Alb.GreetingsMinstrel.Description.Main', 'Greetings I can tell you about your specializations, [Stealth], [Slash], [Thrust], [Instruments], let me know when you are [done].', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMinstrelDescriptionSlash', 'Alb.GreetingsMinstrel.Description.Slash', 'Slash is a basic weaponry skill. Each point you place into it will increase your damage with a slashing weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to slashing weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Stealth], [Slash], [Thrust], [Instruments], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMinstrelDescriptionStealth', 'Alb.GreetingsMinstrel.Description.Stealth', 'Stealth is your ability to move around unseen. The higher you train it, the better you will become. It also contains abilities like Safefall, which allows you to fall from great distances unharmed. What else can I tell you about? [Stealth], [Slash], [Thrust], [Instruments], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsMinstrelDescriptionThrust', 'Alb.GreetingsMinstrel.Description.Thrust', 'Thrust is a basic weaponry skill. Each point you place into it will increase your damage with a thrusting weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to thrusting weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Stealth], [Slash], [Thrust], [Instruments], or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
