	('greetingsNecromancerStory', 'Alb.GreetingsNecromancer.Story', 'Welcome Necromancer. Arawn has been watching you. Whispers have come to us in our... rest. You have made a wise choice in becoming a Necromancer. Allow me to explain some of the powers we have been gifted with, and after I can share with you a reward.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
