	('greetingsPaladinDescriptionCrush', 'Alb.GreetingsPaladin.Description.Crush', 'Crush is a basic weaponry skill. Each train you place into it will increase your damage with a crushing weapon. At different levels of training you will acquire combat styles. These styles will be unique to crushing weapons. What else can I tell you about? [Slash], [Crush], [Thrust], [Two-handed], [Shield], [Chants] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsPaladinDescriptionShield', 'Alb.GreetingsPaladin.Description.Shield', 'Training your shield specialization will increase your ability to block an enemy\'s attacks. What most do not know is, it can also be used offensively in the right situations. Training shield will grant you shield specific combat styles at various levels. What else can I tell you about? [Slash], [Crush], [Thrust], [Two-handed], [Shield], [Chants] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
