	('greetingsReaverDescriptionSoulrending', 'Alb.GreetingsReaver.Description.Soulrending', 'The soulrending specialization holds your magical abilities. The abilities will increase in damage with each train. These abilities include offensive and defensive aura\'s, Lifetaping abilities, and damage over time spells as well as damage adds for your weapon. What else can I tell you about? [Slash], [Crush], [Thrust], [Flexible], [Shield], [Parry], [Soulrending]. Or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
