	('greetingsReaverStory', 'Alb.GreetingsReaver.Story', 'Welcome Reaver. I am Practnum your trainer here in Constantine\'s Sound. I can help you understand the in\'s and out\'s of being a Reaver. You have many specializations available to you. I can help by explaining each one of them to you. When you have a firm grasp in what each does, you will be given a choice of a weapon as a reward.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
