	('greetingsScoutDescriptionBow', 'Alb.GreetingsScout.Description.Bow', 'Training bow as a scout will open up a variety of different shots with your bow. It will also increase the damage those shots will do. What else can I tell you about? [Slash], [Thrust], [Stealth], [Shield], [Bow] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
