	('greetingsScoutStory', 'Alb.GreetingsScout.Story', 'Greetings Scout. I welcome you to Constantine\'s Sound. It takes a sharp eye to join our ranks, and an even sharper mind. You have many specializations available to you. Perhaps it would be best if we went over them together? Afterwards we\'ll see about getting you something better than that practice weapon of yours.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
