	('greetingsSorcererDescriptionBody', 'Alb.GreetingsSorcerer.Description.Body', 'Training body will increase the damage of your life tapping abilities. It will also give you higher damage spells. Also in body are several damage type debuffs, and an area effect root. Toots will hold an enemy in place. What else can I tell you about? [Body], [Matter], [Mind] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsSorcererDescriptionDone', 'Alb.GreetingsSorcerer.Description.Done', 'Very well then, remember you can come to me at any time to ask about your specializations if you need.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsSorcererDescriptionMain', 'Alb.GreetingsSorcerer.Description.Main', 'I can explain all of your specializations for you: [Body], [Matter], [Mind]. Let me know when you are [done].', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsSorcererDescriptionMatter', 'Alb.GreetingsSorcerer.Description.Matter', 'The matter line holds your damage over time (Dot) spells. It also contains a damage and snare spell list. These spells will damage and slow an enemies\' movement speed. Matter also contains instant stat debuff spells. What else can I tell you about? [Body], [Matter], [Mind] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsSorcererDescriptionMind', 'Alb.GreetingsSorcerer.Description.Mind', 'The mind line is one of the sorcerer\'s most powerful lines. It contains area effect mesmerization spells, power regeneration buffs, and a mesemerization dampening spell for you and your group mates. What else can I tell you about? [Body], [Matter], [Mind] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
