	('greetingsTheurgistDescriptionAir', 'Alb.GreetingsTheurgist.Description.Air', 'The air line will open up air pets to the caster. Air pets will melee and instantly stun a target. Air also provides high direct damage spells. Also within the air line are area effect mesmerization spells. What else can I tell you about: [Earth], [Ice], [Air] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsTheurgistDescriptionEarth', 'Alb.GreetingsTheurgist.Description.Earth', 'The earth specialization holds a variety of tools. First, there is an earth pet, whose duration and strength surpasses all other pets. A pulsing blade turn spell that will ward off enemy attacks, and a specialized spell line that increases in damage. What else can I tell you about: [Earth], [Ice], [Air] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsTheurgistDescriptionIce', 'Alb.GreetingsTheurgist.Description.Ice', 'Training ice will open ice pets up to the caster. Ice pets stay close to the caster and will cast ice damage and debuff spells. You will also have your own damage and debuff spells in this line. Ice also comes with an Area effect root spell. What else can I tell you about: [Earth], [Ice], [Air] or are you [done]?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
	('greetingsTheurgistDescriptionMain', 'Alb.GreetingsTheurgist.Description.Main', 'Greetings, I can explain your specializations to you. [Earth], [Ice], [Air], let me know when you are [done].', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
