	('greetingsTheurgistStory', 'Alb.GreetingsTheurgist.Story', 'Greetings and welcome Theurgist, I am Lady Maya, the Theurgist trainer of Constantine\'s Sound. I am here to ensure you understand your specializations. Speak with me and I shall explain all you need to know. Afterwards, I\'ll make sure you are outfitted with a weapon worthy of your skills.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Constantine\'s Sound Quests', NULL),
